Dear {{review.user.profile.salutation_name}},

You have been recommended as a potential peer reviewer for a book submitted to {{press_name}}. The book has been provisionally titled '{{book.title}}’. The contents to review covers the below subject:
 {{book.description}}
 
As part of the editorial process with all {{press_name}} publications, books are reviewed according to the following general principles: 1) conclusions are presented in an appropriate fashion and are supported by the data, 2) that the manuscript is presented in an intelligible fashion, and 3) that the Foreword and Epilogue tie in with the book contents well. We aim to publish books that are solid works of scholarship, irrespective of potential 'impact'.
 
The text is available now for review / will be available from [add start date] [DELETE AS APPROPRIATE]. If you would like to accept or decline this invitation simply click the link below and select the appropriate option. If accepting the invitation you will then have full access to the review files and peer review details.

{{decision_url}}

We are aiming to have the review completed by {{review.due}}, therefore please consider whether this would be possible if accepting the invitation. If you require a different schedule then please let me know.
 
Thank you for considering this request. As always, the efforts of all peer reviewers are greatly appreciated. If you are unable to undertake this review, we would greatly appreciate any thoughts you might have on others who we might approach. 
 
Many thanks for your time and consideration of this invitation,
 
Kind regards,

{{sender.first_name}}
{% if sender %}{{ sender.profile.signature|safe }}{% endif %}

Dear {{review.user.profile.salutation_name}},

You have been recommended as a potential reviewer for a book proposal submitted to {{press_name}}. The proposal has been provisionally titled '{{book.title}}’. 
 
All books proposed to {{press_name}} are reviewed prior to full submission. We are therefore looking for an expert in this field to comment on the content of the proposal. In general, we are looking for a brief comment on the following principals: 1) are there any significant weaknesses/errors included in the book details?, 2) is there a need for such a book/would researchers find this useful?, and 3) are there suggestions on how the book content could be improved? We aim to publish books that are solid works of scholarship, irrespective of potential 'impact'.
 
The proposal details are available now for review. Please accept or decline this invitation by clicking the link below and select the appropriate option. If accepting the invitation you will then have full access to the proposal details.

{{review_url}}

We are aiming to have the proposal review completed by {{review.due}}, therefore please consider whether this would be possible if accepting the invitation. If you require a different schedule then please let me know.
 
Thank you for considering this request. As always, the efforts of all reviewers are greatly appreciated. If you are unable to undertake this review, we would greatly appreciate any thoughts you might have on others who we might approach. 
 
Many thanks for your time and consideration of this invitation,
 
Kind regards,
{% if proposal.requestor %}
{{proposal.requestor.first_name}}
{% else %}
{{press_name}}
{% endif %}

Dear {{submission.owner.profile.salutation_name}},

I have uploaded the most recent version of the contract to our editorial system. Please could you log into your account to review the details and sign off the document. If you would like to discuss any of the clauses prior to signing it off then please let me know.

Kind regards,

{{sender.first_name}}
{% if sender %}{{ sender.profile.signature|safe }}{% endif %}

Dear {{review.user.profile.salutation_name}},

This is a quick email to see if the review for {{book.title}} is on target to meet the agreed deadline of  {{review.due|date:""c""}}. If getting the review back to us by this date is looking unlikely, please could you get in touch at your earliest convenience?

Many thanks,

{{sender.first_name}}
{% if sender %}{{ sender.profile.signature|safe }}{% endif %}

